    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hairstyling process in which hair is parted into rows and braided firmly on the surface of the scalp into various patterns.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
